Fast_Healing.help: You regenerate health faster than the average person and are more resistant to regeneration debuffs.

Reconstruction.help: You concentrate for a few moments and heal yourself. This healing also leaves you briefly more resistant to toxic damage.

Quick_Recovery.help: You recover endurance faster than the average person.

Dull_Pain.help: Using ancient techniques, you make yourself more resilient to pain, which takes the form of an increase in your maximum health.

Moment_of_Glory.help: You gain resistance to and defense against all damage types except psionic, recover endurance more quickly, and are highly resistant to knocks, repels, sleeps, stuns, immobilizes, and holds.
Moment_of_Glory.shortHelp: Self,+RES(All except Psionic), +RES(Knock, Repel, Stun, Sleep, Immobilize, Hold), +DEF(All except Psionics), +Recovery
